{
  "stem": "24364.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And everybody was pretty restless and pretty unhappy and not knowing what was going to become of us, because we were-- had been told originally that we never could go back to Palestine, that we were forever banned from there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So nobody really knew what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The war was going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We-- most of us did not have any letters from our parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I-- after '42, everything stopped, because most of our parents were deported at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And so we had no idea what was happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I had relatives in Palestine, and apparently my parents had at some time or other given them some money, if-- because at that time they thought, obviously, that I was going to get to Palestine, so that I had-- that I would have some money once I got there.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So this way, I could get some money from my relatives from Palestine, because they could send the money to Mauritius.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And my brother was in Palestine at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He was younger than I and he had been able to go legally on a children's certificate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he spent the war with my relatives in-- in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But obviously, the fact that we never heard from our parents anymore, that really got to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we had-- I think I had forebodings all the time that I'm never going to see them again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In 1942, or even the end-- '40, '41, the end-- it might have been-- no, I think it was '42.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "In 1942, Czech young men had volunteered to go into the Czech army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And it took quite a few months before they were allowed to do so, but finally they were.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
